Introduction

Minji, also known by her full name Park Minji, is a South Korean singer and former member of the girl group SECRET NUMBER.

In 2016, she was a competitor on Produce 101 Season 1. However, she ranked #71 on episode 5 and was eliminated. She was also a competitor on Produce 48 in 2018. However, she ranked #53 on episode 8 and was eliminated. On October 18, 2021, Vine Entertainment announced that Minji, alongside Zuu, would be joining SECRET NUMBER as the group's newest members. She officially debuted as a member on October 27 with the single album "Fire Saturday".

On April 4, 2025, she, alongside members Jinny and Dita, released a collective statement announcing their departures from the group as well as Vine Entertainment.
